1 add parameters to the leap.transformer.arg, then run TransformPreprocess, the new classes are put 
to the tmp/IntermediateCP, and the new parameters are refreshed into leap.transformer.arg
2 run TransformMain, it generates the SPE size and writes it to the leap.recorder.arg
Also, the classes for the recording version and replaying version are generated.
3 run the RecordMain, its argument is in the leap.recorder.arg, however, you may add the arglist manually
for extra arguments.
4 refresh the replay project
5 run the ReplayDriver
